data.description: Say H E L L O to this charming 3 bedroom home that is move-in ready and waiting for YOU! This home has been updated and well maintained. It is perfect for a 1st Time homebuyer or investor looking for a great, move-in ready home.  The roof & fridge were replaced in 2022. A serene & private side patio seating area was also added complete with new patio pavers and a double awning to protect you from the Florida sun. A great outdoor living space to enjoy your morning coffee. Additional items replaced/added over the past 3 years are: blinds, toilet, bathroom pedestal sink, kitchen faucet, utility faucet, AC motor & fan, rain gutters & a storm door. In addition to the 3rd bedroom there is a bonus den and a spacious indoor laundry/utility room that offers extra storage. This home is move-in ready and won’t last long!
